title: 150: Deshaun Watson, 2017 QB class, National Championship recap
itunes:title: 150: Deshaun Watson, 2017 QB class, National Championship recap
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks recap Monday night's NCAA National Championship game between Clemson and Alabama. They discuss Clemson QB Deshaun Watson's performance and his NFL potential. The duo also go over the rest of the 2017 QB class including North Carolina's Mitch Trubisky, DeShone Kizer from Notre Dame and Miami's Brad Kaaya.
